.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnhDscOR.jpg&h=3e555821&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmREMtKQoqvoEMfKMyZg4UPao7jw1b1UPJWshGk29ymCtD?filename=2NWmhfv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NWmhfv.jpg&h=0cb8e5db&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">蘋果同泛民灌輸既意識形態：<br />\n隻毒好撚柒勁，大家要防疫要打針<br />\n就係香港無得救，大家要移民<br />\n唔撚好再反抗，反抗等如送頭無意義<br />\n大家外判抗爭俾國際線，咁就有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a3ec32cf8067fc5d532fbbc3f86fa689d37c0f97","tid":2462511,"uid":389613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:02:52.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好引用 #8，比佢金鋼棒洗版破壞排版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有連尼住幾時班 #8 隻五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da85dfedc7e8b2b0aca6ddf0733f29fc35a3b168","tid":2462511,"uid":139200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:06:47.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n咁睇都理論都make sense<br />\n不嬲都知中共外滙開始有問題<br />\n防港人走資 同 禁大陸人出境<br />\n本身都已經好明顯<br />\n<br />\n新疆棉花 老共無得拆<br />\n禁唔到歐美廠唔用<br />\n而歐美消費者都好大機會唔買新疆產的<br />\n加埋工廠撤退 外滙收入會愈來愈少<br />\n中間可能加埋 禁境內企業滙出外幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終結果一定係武統台灣<br />\n好大機會幾個月就黎"},{"pid":"7e3732be099073dce0fef84e83d9475068fb4a5c","tid":2462511,"uid":389613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"寫今次篇文主因另一 post 有位人兄同我講 西方 重組供應鏈無用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#453 回覆 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/sHkJGvX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/sHkJGvX</a>"},{"pid":"c410253e2205a0bd5959022554fc2c5c9b7432cc","tid":2462